1. *Uspori* pa ćeš stići na vreme. (Slow down and you'll arrive on time.)
2. Motor se *usporio* i zaustavio. (The engine slowed down and stopped.)
3. *Usporila* je korak i zaustavila se. (She slowed down her step and stopped.)
4. Autoput se *usporio* zbog gužve. (The highway slowed down due to traffic.)
5. *Uspori* da ne bi prešla granicu brzine. (Slow down so you don't exceed the speed limit.)